name: Marlee Matlin
bio: Oscar Best Actress | Director | Mom of 4, wife of 1 🤟💜she/her

social_posts.post_text: Happy Hanukkah to you and yours. May your candles burn bright! 🕎🤟🏻❤️🕎

So happy to say it is @aakashar who is celebrating her birthday today! As you see numerous photos, what I love about Alexis is she is game for anything when we are together in person. We play dress up. We get goofy. We pose for pictures when we are tired. Adventure is what we aim for whenever we get together. Alexis, thank YOU for your unconditional love and friendship. I cherish every moment spent with you, near or far. Happy birthday and you know you are loved by me and your posse. 🎂💜🤟🏼🎂💜🤟🏼

#merrychristmas #asl #signlanguage #happyholidays

Image description : Marlee Matlin signs “Merry Christmas” in American Sign Language, then pulls out a red pillow with the word JOY spelled out in ASL

I cannot believe in writing this….it’s my baby girl’s 19th birthday today. All of 19!!!! Isabelle, you are truly an amazing human being who I truly am in awe of. I am SO HAPPY you are my daughter. I love you so VERY much and I truly care a great deal for you. You bring me joy and happiness on a daily basis even when you don’t listen to me at times. Now you’re 19, you have so much ahead of you that I can see GREAT opportunities that will come your way. You are SO BEAUTIFUL…inside and out. I love love love LOVE you baby girl. @isabelle.grandalski #birthdaygirl #19 #funniestgirliknow #bestyoungestdaughter #duck 🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼💜💜💜🌟🌟🌟
Love my family! #isabellesbirthdayboatparty @isabelle.grandalski @sarahgrandalski @brandongrandalskii @tylergrandalski #kevin #blessed 🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼

How sad I was to find out about the passing of #VivienneWestwood. Such a groundbreaking force in the fashion world. And she designed this sustainable dress I wore at @theacademy Awards in 2021; I never felt more beautiful. RIP, dear Vivienne. Photo by @cpizzello

I LOVED wearing my beautiful sustainably designed dress made by @viviennewestwood. I’ll cherish that memory forever. RIP Vivienne.
Video by @brettglam

Remarkable. Fearless. Assured and laser focused in her interviews, she broke through every barrier, paving the way for every woman journalist who followed. What an honor it was to be interviewed by her on @theviewabc. RIP Barbara Walters.
2022..A year to remember. #oscars #academyawards #codamovie #bestpicture #sagawards #bestensemble #accused #director #boardofgovernors
Happy Birthday @davidbowie
I adore @brettglam.  His beauty expertise is magic. 💜🤟🏼💜🤟🏼

Today is truly a very sad day. My friend Vae has been taken from us to go to heaven. She truly made me laugh every time we got together over the years. We always made a habit to take good/silly pictures each time we saw each other. These two pictures were taken this past October. Fly high, VAE…you’ll always have a place in my heart. Oh yeah, make everyone laugh up above. 🙏💜🤟🏼REST IN PEACE, my girl.

Remembering @marshavae all the while being mindful that I need to remember every day, “One day at a time.” #soberlife #rememberingafriend❤️ 🤟🏻 ❤️ 🤟🏻 ❤️

Marlee Matlin is wearing a blue sweater/hoodie, sitting at her desk. Behind her are various photographs and personal mementos.
Honored. And even better - all the films I’ll be screening, Sundance is providing open / closed captions.

This picture of VAE and I makes me laugh. Me holding on to her for dear life! We were posing for a group picture and I just held on to her for no reason! Maybe subconsciously showing my love for her! RIP Miss Vae. #2022 #rosellihouse #girlshousenightout #marshavaegoeken 🦋🤟🏼🙏

So excited to be on @KellyClarksonTV on Thursday, January 12! We talked about our love for tattoos (we compare numbers), we talked about the wonderful year CODA has had (in no small part to Kelly!) & my new adventure as a director for @AccusedFOX airing on January 24 on @FOXTV!
My favorite Oscars moment - As a newly installed member of the Board of Governors, I’m excited to celebrate 95 years of #Oscars with @TheAcademy!

This beauty is our oldest daughter who is celebrating her 27th birthday! Sarah!!!!!! You bring such joy and happiness into our lives. Your personality is top notch and your beauty, inside and out does not go unnoticed. You show care, support, love, loyalty and so much more to so many people. You bring light as soon as you walk into a room and people literally stop doing whatever they’re doing and look at you, telling themselves, she is beautiful. Happy birthday baby girl and we LOVE you! And can you for the life of me, stop flipping off? 🤣🤣🤣 APOLOGIES TO SOME WHO GET OFFENDED, but then I can say I am responsible for it! 🤷‍♀️🤷‍♀️😬🌟🎂🌟🎂🌟🎂💜🤟🏼💜🤟🏼💜🤟🏼💜🤟🏼 @sarahgrandalski #birthdaygirl #oldestoffour #kevin 🌟🤟🏼💜🤟🏼

Two years ago I was part of my first @sundanceorg film CODA. Now I’m proud to be here as a member of the US Dramatic Competiton jury! What a wonderful journey it’s been. Thank you Sundance!
#sundancefilmfestival #sundance2023 #coda #parkcity  #snow #film #independentfilm
Love being reunited with @hayleyaston here at Sundance (we go back to #switchedatbirth days!)
Happy birthday to the man who always had my back from the day I was born to the day he passed. I still feel his love for me from above. Happy birthday! #donmatlin 🎂🤟🏼🎂🤟🏼

This is “Ava’s Story” part of the NEW groundbreaking court drama series, ACCUSED, on TOMORROW night, January 24 on @foxtv and @hulu  the next day. It is one of the most COMPELLING stories you’ve NEVER seen and I felt so privileged  to direct my actors, Deaf and hearing! #accusedfox #foxtv #authenticity #inclusion #access #equity

No one could’ve told this story better, @themarleematlin. 

📺: #AccusedOnFOX

CODA finally got the @sundanceorg Film Festival screening that it was meant to have in 2021, on its way to @theacademy Awards. It all started here in Park City and we were so grateful to finally be able enjoy it on the big screen at Eccles. And though @emiliajonesy @danielndurant @ederbez and @amy4syth couldn’t be there, they were there in spirit with us. Best of all, we got to celebrate with an audience and we will never forget that. I love you all forever! ❤️🤟🏻❤️🤟🏻❤️🤟🏻 #coda #sundancefilmfestival
I’m very lucky to be standing in between two gifted actors. #henrywinkler @troykotsur
A day late but I’m sure @johnmaucere will forgive me. Look how young we look! And he STILL looks young to the day! Happy birthday, my friend. 🎂🌟🤟🏼
Happy birthday Captain Kevin! Lots of love to you! #kevin #twogoofballsonaboat 🎂🌟🤟🏼

My VERY handsome birthday man is accompanying me to the Academy Nominee’s Luncheon. Lucky me, eh? #kevin  @lafayette148ny @dolcegabbana @hanut101 @retrouvai @msjordanjohnson @craiggangi @hayleyaston @theacademy

I’m so excited to be partnered with @MGMstudios - producers of The Voice to bring the next big talent show for ASL interpreters and performers to your screen. If you loved what you saw with Rihanna’s ASL performer at the Super Bowl - just you wait. #talentshow #ASL

At it again with my brilliant and dear friend @lukewessman…perseverance..four of my kids birth flower in a bunch…and Angel wings in memory of my mother and father. #libby #donald @bikeshedmotoco 🤟🏼 #notstoppinghere #14 #yesithurtalot #worthit
My BESTEST SONS! Happy National Son’s Day! It is actually EVERYDAY that I celebrate my two sons whom I am SO proud of. @brandongrandalskii @tylergrandalski 💜🤟🏼🌟💜🤟🏼🌟💜🤟🏼#gratefultobetheirmom

Judith Heumann was a fearless champion for the rights of people with disabilities and millions of people who have faced barriers owe her a debt of gratitude. (You can see her journey in the @theacademy award nominated documentary, Crip Camp).
🤟🏻 Judy. I will always remember you as my hero and my friend.
RIP Judy Heumann 🤟🏻 #beingheumann #beingheumannmemoir  #cripcamp #heumannperspective

Missing my mother sorely on this Mother’s Day and everyday. Cherish your time with your mother while she is around. Happy Mother’s Day! #libbymatlin 🤟🏼💜🤟🏼💜

Our son Brandon graduated with a Bachelors of Arts in Public Relations at Marquette University this morning! And I had the honor of receiving Doctor of Fine Arts! I delivered the commencement speech to the graduates in which made me so happy. @brandongrandalskii @marquetteuniversity #2023 CONGRATS to every graduate this year! #proudmomanddad @sarahgrandalski @tylergrandalski @isabelle.grandalski @liztannebaum @thewendyadams3 @charlotte.culpepper @kimberly_grandalski 🌟🌟💜💜

Happy to say today is my bestie’s birthday! Wendy, you bring me so much joy ( and my family and so many people too ) and you truly have a heart of gold. Your empathy is so genuine. I love laughing with you. I love talking with you. I love spending time with you whether it is on FT or in person. Your friendship is truly valuable to me and I appreciate you. I love your honesty and especially your humor.  Never change, girl. I love you to the moon and back a zillion-plus times. Happy birthday! Lots of love! 🎂🌟🎂🌟🤟🏼🤟🏼💜💜🤟🏼🤟🏼 @thewendyadams3
Proud as F**k. 🌈🌈🌈🤟🏼🤟🏼

I was proud to do this shoot on behalf of Alzheimer’s Awareness.

“From sleek and sophisticated 👠 to partying in purple 🎉, Academy Award winner and #ENDALZ Celebrity Champion @themarleematlin is going purple for Alzheimer’s & Brain Awareness Month. Join Marlee and #GoPurple to raise Alzheimer’s awareness in June.”

It was a @switchedatbirthtv reunion on the picket lines in support of our creator @lizzyweiss and all the wonderful writers and producers and members of the @wgaeast @wgawest @wgastrikeunite @wgadailypicket #rebootsab #rebootswitchedatbirth

The one and only @jackjason is celebrating his birthday! Help me give him a huge holler to wish him the happiest birthday! Jack!!! There are countless photos of us but I chose these because they’re recent and we look pretty! 🤣 Happy birthday, my sweet friend…me and my family love you very much! Now go celebrate YOU! 🎂🤟🏼🎂🤟🏼🎂🤟🏼
Happy 1st anniversary to my brother Marc and his husband Jay! I love you both so much!!! 💜💜💜💜💜🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼💜💜🌈🌈

I cannot imagine anyone but Kevin being the father of our four children. I truly struck gold with this guy. Kevin puts up with my parenting style in which I’m grateful for because it is wacky but I continue to be in awe of him whenever he is in a father mode. He is a total natural. It is ALL him. An original, 1000000%. Happy Father’s Day, Kev and to all the  fathers out there. AND to my Dad who is up in heaven…I miss you Dad. It hurts but I continue to smile whenever I think of you which is so very often. 🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼 @sarahgrandalski @brandongrandalskii @tylergrandalski @isabelle.grandalski #kmsbti
These two cuties ( great niece and nephew ) are now 6 and 4 years old! Love them so much! #HannahNoah

I am VERY blessed to call this lady my mother in law! @charlotte.culpepper is celebrating a huge birthday milestone today! Can’t wait to celebrate YOU! I love you so much! 🎂🤟🏼🎂🤟🏼🎂🎂 #kevin’smother #luckiestdaughterinlawever #youngatheart #79+1

Had such a great GREAT time celebrating my mother in law’s 40+10+9+15+6 birthday! LOVED being with family and friends. THANK YOU for those who traveled from afar to make my MIK SO happy and beyond! I know her heart is FULL from all the love from everyone who were there! We missed sone family members and friends who couldn’t be with us. We love you @charlotte.culpepper 🎂🎂💜💜🤟🏼🤟🏼and 🤟🏼🤟🏼 to @kimberly_grandalski my sis in law!!! 🤟🏼🤟🏼

It’s my son Tyler’s TWENTY FIRST birthday! Gosh! How time really flies! Tyler, you have been such a joy in my life the second you were born. Your wicked sense of humor is a PLUS. Your passion for so many things truly brings out the best of you. You are fierce, loyal, honest, authentic, funny, handsome, smart and talented in so many ways. Dad and I are very proud of you. Can’t wait to see what the future brings to you ( it already started anyway! ) Happy birthday Tyler and now you can get rid of all the ID’s you’ve been using to purchase liquor and use your actual license! I love you ZILLIONS times from the moon and back! @tylergrandalski 🎂🤟🏼🎂🤟🏼🎂🤟🏼 #7-18-02 #birthdayboy #legal #chicago #kevin #morepicturestocome❤️
GenZ. #birthdayboytoday #21 #notmycar @tylergrandalski

It happened, FINALLY! After three-four years of talking on zoom/FaceTime…we met today IN THE FLESH. My goodness, @mjgrant_ is an absolute gem. Truly beautiful in and out and I am SO happy to call her my dear friend. Love you, Ms. MJ. 🤟🏼💜🤟🏼💜
I support SAG AFTRA.
We are Chicago @sagaftra STRONG
Happy birthday Mom, I trust you’re celebrating with Dad and everyone else up in heaven. I miss you sorely and I love you very much. #libbymatlin #93 🎂🤟🏼🤟🏼🎂🤟🏼xoxo

A blast from the past. Childhood friends gathered today reminiscing our fun times as kids. What an absolute treat it was to be with these friends who I’ve known for 45+ years. Amazing how we all still look GREAT!😂🤪😂🤪 #mitchchuckmarkliztonymarleehoward #chicago #memories #blessed 🤟🏼

It’s RUTHIE’S birthday! Help me give @drruthiemd a HUGE birthday shout out because she truly deserves it!!! Yo girl, my only SOUL SISTER, you must know how much I love you. All the 36 years we’ve known each other has been nothing short of love, laughter, tears,  and so much more. Your loyalty to our friendship is one that is fiercely honest and I love you for that. Happy birthday, my girl. 🎂💜🎂💜🤟🏼🤟🏼#august11th

Hey people! This beauty standing right next to me has been my “ girl half “ for 53 years. Today @liztannebaum is celebrating her birthday! Sis, there is no other person that is like you. You are one of a kind, a gem and you bring so much love and light everywhere you go. I am SO lucky to call you my sister. For life. Always. Forever. Happy birthday and have a beautiful day celebrating YOU! I love you!!!!! 🎂🌟🤟🏼🎂💜🤟🏼🎂💜🤟🏼 #8/26/23 #bff
Happiest of birthdays to my Sister in Law! So happy you married my brother Eric! Love you Gloria! @glo360realestatebrokercompass @eric_matlin 🎂🤟🏼🎂🤟🏼
Where were you on August 29, 1993? I married my love on that day. 30 years ago! I am still on cloud nine being married to my one and only love. #kevin #morepicturestocome 🤟🏼💜🤟🏼💜🤟🏼💜
Today is the launch of the NFL ASL collection by LOVE SIGN for all 32 teams. Merch with the LOVE SIGN ASL design is now available on t shirts and hats on the nflshop.com. Link in my bio.
Bears VS Packers! Who do you think I’m rooting for?? DA BEARS! Loving my @lovesign.asl shirt! @alexis.kashar @nfl #chicagogirlforever @chicagobears 🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼 @thewendyadams3 #bestfriend

Today (9-12) is my son, Brandon’s 23rd birthday! B, I truly am the luckiest mother in the world to have a son and that is YOU. You have brought me ( and of course Dad ) nothing but happiness, pride and respect for you. I LOVE that we both share our love for sports especially Chicago teams and somewhat California teams too! Your humor is infectious. Your kindness for people makes me feel very good. You’ve taught me to be a mother in so many ways and yes, so do your siblings too. Thank you for being YOU. Happy birthday son and I love you so so so much! 🎂💜🤟🏼🎂💜🤟🏼 @brandongrandalskii
One day at a time.

Happy National Daughter’s Day. I am the LUCKIEST mother to these daughters of mine. Truly thankful they are in my life. They inspire me everyday and they are my biggest cheerleaders who keep me grounded and who have faith in me. I hope to make them proud just being their mother, well…crazy mother. 🤣 I love you two SO much…thank you for giving me unconditional love and I wake up everyday feeling blessed to be able to watch you two grow into incredible ladies. Your beauty ( in and out ) just makes me smile! 🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼 @sarahgrandalski @isabelle.grandalski
How fun is this when we are getting our hair pampered at the same time and place! @jillianseely @agnesohairdesign @liztannebaum #sisters #hairgoals love you @craiggangi #touchup @jillianseely

Happy National Son’s Day to my COOLEST AWESOME HANDSOME SMART FUNNIEST sons of mine! ( and my husband’s too lol! ) I am SO PROUD to be your mom! I love you both to the moon and back ZILLION times! And yes, happy to do your laundry whenever I am in town! All I need are hugs as a thank you! @brandongrandalskii @tylergrandalski 🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼 #nationalsonsday

I had the GREATEST pleasure being on the ice @nhlblackhawks !!! I hit the puck to the best of my ability and it almost made it through. Dang it BUT the best part was being with everyone in the stadium and seeing my son there! @brandongrandalskii #chicagogirlforever #mortongrove @liztannebaum @eric_matlin @zackmatlin ❤️🖤🤍❤️🖤🤍 Special shout-out to the folks that took great care of me and my family! 🤟🏼

Today’s my dad’s 10th anniversary of his passing. The photo of the two of us was taken about three months before he died. It is one of my absolute favorite photos. Also I had his writing tattooed on my ankle/foot. Missing him so very much and he continues to live in my heart everyday, and forever. #daddysgirl #donaldmatlin #10-4-13 @lukewessman ( thank you Luke for tattooing this beautiful piece ) 🤟🏼🤟🏼
GO BEARS!!!!! #chicagogirl @lovesign.asl @chicagobears @nfl DA BEARS 🧡💙🤍🧡💙🤍

Thinking of our families, friends and people in Israel. Condolences to the families and friends of those who perished and those who are injured. And those who are missing, I pray they are returned back home safely. Kindness is what we need to be more than ever. Hug your loved ones. Be kind all around. 🇮🇱

She was my first onscreen mother and she was celebrated way before we worked together eventually garnering including three @theacademy Award nominations. I’ll never forget her kind, sweet spirit and fierce talent. RIP Piper Laurie. 🤟🏻❤️

What an AMAZING weekend at UO with our youngest daughter!!! Family weekend turned out to be wild but worth every moment here in Eugene! Love you @isabelle.grandalski and loved seeing your friends everywhere we went! #kkg #sororitylife #universityoforegon GO DUCKS! #Frames #loveyoujohannamilliebutter #kevin 💚💛💚💛💚💛💚💛

I got chills watching this. THANK YOU  @governorjanetmills for your powerful acknowledgment of the ASL interpreter. And thank you @cnn for showing the interpreter on screen the whole time. #lewiston strong #deafcommunity strong 🤟🏻

Happy Birthday to #henrywinkler who has been like a second father to me all these years. And he is truly the nicest person in Hollywood. Now go out and get his book - “Being Henry…The Fonz and Beyond”! 🤟🏻🎂🤟🏻🎂.
#birthday #fonz #happydays😊

My heart is very heavy. My dearest brother in law, Dr. Jay Goldstein passed away this morning. Jay and my brother were together for 40 BEAUTIFUL years and got married last year. Jay ( to my right ) made my brother the happiest man. Jay gave my brother nothing but love, humor and life. Jay will FOREVER have a place in my heart as well as Kevin’s and our children. We love you Marc and Skippy and Joey. RIP Jay. 💜🤟🏼💜🤟🏼💜🤟🏼
My girls. Unconditional love. A rarity of its kind. @liztannebaum @alexis.kashar @thewendyadams3
#happythanksgivng!

This is one of my favorite pictures of me and my bestie @alexis.kashar who is celebrating her birthday today! (12/21) Alexis, you continue to inspire me in every way, shape and form. You empower me in all directions and I thank you for that. Happy birthday, babe. Celebrate to the max as you deserve the best of everything in life. Good health, happiness and love to you. I love you! 🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼🎂🎂🌟🌟

A shout out to our baby daughter, Isabelle for her birthday TODAY! CANNOT BELIEVE how you are all of 20  years old. Time truly flew by, in the blink of an eye. We are so proud of you in everything you do ( even when you are tailgating at school 🤪 GO DUCKS )!! You continue to be one of the funniest, smartest, resilient and most beautiful human we know. We Love you so much!!! Happy birthday sweet baby girl, and now please go clean your room! 🎂🎂🤟🏼🤟🏼🩷🩷🩷🌟🌟 @isabelle.grandalski @kappakappagamma #birthdaygirl #kevin

Text: one Day at a Time is one of my favorite tattoos that I have. It means a great deal to me. Today I have 37!years of sobriety. Grateful for being sober. Grateful. I love you.
#sober #grateful #onedayatatime
